=========================================
Ztcpdump for the Bivio 7000 Series  
=========================================


-----------------------------------------
Introduction
-----------------------------------------

Ztcpdump is Tcpdump linked against the zero copy 
library. The only reason for calling the application
Ztcpdump is because the default Tcpdump also resides on
the system. 


-----------------------------------------
Notes
-----------------------------------------


-----------------------------------------
Installation
-----------------------------------------

1. rpm -Uvh ztcpdump-4.0.0-1.B7000.ppc.rpm


-----------------------------------------
Starting
-----------------------------------------

1. Start Ztcpdump running on the application CPU's

        nrsp start ztcpdump



